trans-unit.source: Specifies the types of output quality for a print device.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvilke typer utdata kvalitet for skriver.

trans-unit.source: Use the values of this type primarily for these purposes: - As members of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.OutputQualityCapability%2A> collection, which is a property of <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>, these values indicate the types of output quality that a printer supports.
trans-unit.target: Bruk verdiene i denne typen først og fremst for dette formålet: – som medlemmer av den <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.OutputQualityCapability%2A>samling, som er en egenskap av <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>, disse verdiene indikerer typer utdata kvalitet som støtter en skriver.</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> </xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.OutputQualityCapability%2A>

trans-unit.source: - As the value of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.OutputQuality%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>, they direct a printer to produce a particular quality.
trans-unit.target: -Som verdien for den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.OutputQuality%2A>for en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>, de direkte en skriver til å produsere et bestemt kvalitet.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.OutputQuality%2A>

trans-unit.source: The `Unknown` value is never used in properties of <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> objects.
trans-unit.target: Den `Unknown` verdien aldri er brukt i egenskapene for <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>objekter.</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>

trans-unit.source: You should never set a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> property to `Unknown`.

If some other <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> producing application has created a *PrintTicket document* that sets the output quality feature to an unrecognized option (that is, an option that is not defined in the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)), then a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> object in your application that is constructed with that document will have `Unknown` as the value of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.OutputQuality%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis noen andre <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>produserer applikasjonen er opprettet en *PrintTicket dokumentet* som angir funksjonen utdata kvaliteten til et ugjenkjennelig alternativ (som er et alternativ som ikke er definert i den [Skriv ut skjemaet](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)), og deretter en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>objektet i programmet som er laget med dette dokumentet har `Unknown` som verdien for den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.OutputQuality%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.OutputQuality%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: Although the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> classes cannot be inherited, you can extend the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397) to recognize print device features that are not accounted for in the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> or <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> classes.
trans-unit.target: Selv om den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>og <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>klasser kan arves, kan du utvide den [skrive ut skjemaet](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397) ikke gjenkjenne trykt enhetsfunksjoner som ikke blir inkludert i den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>eller <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>klasser.</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: For more information see [NOTINBUILD: How to: Extend the Print Schema and Create New Print System Classes](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a3600218-1ea5-478a-9853-6560464f2885).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon se [NOTINBUILD: slik: utvide Skriv ut skjemaet og opprette nye utskrift systemklasser](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a3600218-1ea5-478a-9853-6560464f2885).

trans-unit.source: ## Notes on OutputQuality.Photographic Starting with the [!INCLUDE[net_v461](~/add/includes/net-v461-md.md)], the output quality obtained with the Photographic value is improved (compared to previous versions of the .NET Framework) when printing to a GDI-based printer and when running on Windows 7 and earlier versions of the Windows operating system.
trans-unit.target: ## Merknader i OutputQuality.Photographic med start av [!INCLUDE[net_v461](~/add/includes/net-v461-md.md)], utdata kvaliteten innhentet med verdien Photographic forbedret (sammenlignet med tidligere versjoner av .NET Framework) når skriver til en GDI-baserte skriver og kjører på Windows 7 og tidligere versjoner av Windows-operativsystemet.

trans-unit.source: Producing documents with better output quality requires larger print spooler files and longer wait times.
trans-unit.target: Produserer dokumenter med bedre utdata kvalitet krever større trykt køen filer og lengre ventetid.

trans-unit.source: If these side effects are undesirable, you can instead use the High value.
trans-unit.target: Hvis disse bivirkninger uønsket, kan du i stedet bruke høy verdi.

trans-unit.source: Automatically selects a quality type that is based on the contents of a print job.
trans-unit.target: Velger automatisk en kvaliteten-type som er basert på innholdet i en utskriftsjobben.
